\ MiniForth New Features Test

." Testing Floats:" CR
3.14 2.0 * F. CR
10.5 2.5 / F. CR
1.0 2.0 + F. CR

." Testing Strings:" CR
s" Hello " s" World" S+ .S DROP CR
s" MiniForth" SLEN . CR
s" Programming" 3 5 SSUB .S DROP CR

." Testing File I/O:" CR
s" test.txt" s" rw" FOPEN
DUP 0 > IF
    DUP s" File content" SLEN 0 DO
        DUP 72 FWRITE DROP \ H
        DUP 69 FWRITE DROP \ E
        DUP 76 FWRITE DROP \ L
        DUP 76 FWRITE DROP \ L
        DUP 79 FWRITE DROP \ O
    LOOP
    FCLOSE
    ." File written." CR
ELSE
    ." Failed to open file." CR
    DROP
THEN

." Testing Error Reporting (this should fail with line/col):" CR
: FAIL-WORD 1 0 / ;
FAIL-WORD
